---
title: Spiced Pork Schnitzel & Oven-Baked Wedges with Celery Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: It’s time for another twist on a schnitzel! These tender pieces of pork are coated in a golden crumb with Mumbai spices throughout. We’ve kept the sides simple and classic, because really, how do you compete with wedges and slaw for the perfect schnitzel accompaniments.
